comments: Great teacher, I have nothing but good things to say about her. Only, she is so damn hot! It was very difficult to focus in her class. Seriously, I was so distracted that I felt like dropping the class. Once you lay eyes on her, you\'ll know what I am talking about. On a serious note, the woman can teach.

Erin Rody is somewhat of a new professor, at first i knew i was going to enjoy the course because she could speak clearly and eficiently, got the point across very well and is a very nice lady. do not hesitate to take this course. Oh yeah, she is a gorgeous women too!
